# Aurigraph DLT Code Ownership
# =============================
# This file defines code ownership for the Aurigraph DLT repository.
# Owners are automatically requested for review when relevant files are changed.
#
# Format: <pattern> @owner1 @owner2
# Order matters: later patterns take precedence over earlier ones.
#
# Teams:
# @Aurigraph-DLT-Corp/core-team        - Core blockchain developers
# @Aurigraph-DLT-Corp/frontend-team    - Portal and UI developers
# @Aurigraph-DLT-Corp/devops-team      - DevOps and infrastructure
# @Aurigraph-DLT-Corp/security-team    - Security specialists
# @Aurigraph-DLT-Corp/qa-team          - Quality assurance

